===Etymology===
[[File:Periodic table.svg|thumb|The periodic table of the [[element]]s. See [[:Appendix:Chemical elements]].]]

The table is termed “periodic” because it follows the [[periodic law]]&nbsp;– when [[chemical element]]s are arranged in order of increasing [[atomic number]], elements with similar [[property|properties]] [[recur]] at [[interval]]s.

